divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside my apartment on my cell phone and I told the person on the other end that there was something in the sky. I immediately went inside and grabbed my camera and began taking pictures. I know I went out with a friend that night and took the camera. THe next day when I checked the pics, the camera appeared to be burned of fried on the bottom. BUT the memory card was fine. There were only pictures of the ufo in question, not any pictures from the night out. I dont remember taking as many pics as I did and I do not remember ever zooming in on the objects but yet that appears to be what I have pics of.
